    "Add 4 cups of water to the pressure cooker.",
    "Add the grass-fed beef strips and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the paella rice and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Close the lid and pressure cook at 15 PSI for 10 minutes.",
    "Remove the pressure cooker from the heat and let the pressure release naturally.",
